title: EU to finance purchase, delivery of weapons and equipment to Ukraine, announces fresh sanctions against Russia - ThePrint
content: EU to finance purchase, delivery of weapons and equipment to Ukraine, announces fresh sanctions against Russia  ThePrint
description: Brussels [Belgium], February 27 (ANI): The European Union on Sunday (local time) said that it will finance the purchase and delivery of weapons and equipment to Ukraine and also announced a slew of fresh sanctions against Russia. “We are stepping up our support for Ukraine. For the first time, the EU will finance the purchase […]
